{"tid":105393,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【家長呢？】驚嚇現場！ 6歲大陸妹踎馬路小便被輾死","createTime":"2017-02-03T00:18:10.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-03T05:40:28.000Z","uid":122,"like":41,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"568ddf1b108a4fecb24e143ae2415ddd37f36213","tid":105393,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T00:18:10.000Z","msg":"<strong>【家長呢？】驚嚇現場！ 6歲妹踎馬路小便被輾死</strong><br />\n<br />\n2017-02-03 00:50:00 HKT<br />\n<br />\n江西贛州周二（1月31日）發生一宗巴士輾死女童慘劇。當日下午2時33分左右，一名6歲女童獨自走到馬路上蹲下小便，遭一輛停站接載客人的巴士輾壓，途人發現後，趕忙將她從巴士底抱出送院，惜女童最終傷重不治。<br />\n<br />\n警方指，當時巴士司機因見路邊有2名客人揮手示意要上車，便打算停靠路旁，未料卻輾過了蹲着小便的女童，她被送到鄉衞生院後身亡。目前，巴士司機已因涉嫌交通肇事被刑拘。<br />\n<br />\n女童被輾壓的全程被附近閉路電視拍下，畫面曝光後，引來網民熱議，有人驚呼：「太恐怖了，希望小女孩安息！」但更多人則認為是女童的家長，沒有妥善照顧女童才致釀成悲劇：「父母呢......為甚麼在路邊？撒尿？哎，小孩子的父母也有責任！」「監戶人到哪裡去了？孩子為甚麼要在公路上小便？」"},{"pid":"3b9c035ff646b71149b3a98169e231388729df96","tid":105393,"uid":22949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T00:23:04.000Z","msg":"蚹蛤蟈蜻"},{"pid":"b1f064e7d5e97d71a154d001e0063110798f9664","tid":105393,"uid":70361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T00:33:36.000Z","msg":"這就是中國"},{"pid":"62c5fcbcb79e86dc007dfa35ef75b32a5d00233b","tid":105393,"uid":12755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T00:37:40.000Z","msg":"Rip！下世投胎好住好人家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"495643d9efde41de8af6bf752ab44fac8ab2d5fb","tid":105393,"uid":32325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T00:39:04.000Z","msg":"會唔會係特登教個女去馬路屙尿屈賠償<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba0a4fd57cce0ece9b14d10e2ffe956fbe508ef7","tid":105393,"uid":36901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T00:43:45.000Z","msg":"個老母冇睇住細路<br />\n個細佬冇人教佢唔可以隨街小便<br />\n個司機埋站冇睇清楚就鏟埋去<br />\n<br />\n三樣野是但唔中一樣件事都可以避免<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0304194f430472c990b38ed632554fe2a8c087c3","tid":105393,"uid":22553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T00:47:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>會唔會係特登教個女去馬路屙尿屈賠償<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n家屬: 應該起曬圍欄隔住條馬路同行人，防止比人行出馬路，一定係政府責任，要求賠償<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86921a8ea5fcc7901e9e79f962798c540155e8b8","tid":105393,"uid":12980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T00:50:08.000Z","msg":"抵撚死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"005f93363c42d4f023b798b37e8ba9baa1e5a672","tid":105393,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T00:51:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91dbc1304ff04aa245a1b37b2f5a451f259a961f","tid":105393,"uid":21398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T00:56:38.000Z","msg":"無家長？你還有黨呀！"},{"pid":"c7919314e431cdd1a5786f67f8be3cd424effc72","tid":105393,"uid":81345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T01:00:27.000Z","msg":"死左個女?仲有黨呀。"},{"pid":"8d68bf7159fb952b758036929ce30b8875b8978d","tid":105393,"uid":32619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T01:01:37.000Z","msg":"佢老母而家笑到瞓唔著啦<br />\n中國人生女第一日就想佢死 而家仲可以R賠償 lum lum 脷 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46e3cf8ee9fe8ed8d0829abaad62e7cb92e2c4b6","tid":105393,"uid":8048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T01:04:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"964f4f529bf849bc6184fba003b2eedfde455c5b","tid":105393,"uid":35478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T01:04:24.000Z","msg":"[又死一件]<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />?"},{"pid":"6af632cbcfa0205d97f79780c9182e1b79a09b53","tid":105393,"uid":41821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T01:05:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ba2ab09a4e6e55f9723cec37ec0bfa28f0ceae2","tid":105393,"uid":60655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T01:06:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佢老母而家笑到瞓唔著啦<br />\n中國人生女第一日就想佢死 而家仲可以R賠償 lum lum 脷 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔洗養大件蝕本貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44e42b1d0ea749de1e6460212463d5494e25c242","tid":105393,"uid":73262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T01:11:34.000Z","msg":"巴士司機簡直無法無天， 大陸街邊痾屎痾尿大撚晒架嘛， 阻住人痾尿 仲撞撚死人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8859966b3d404b75c5b8ca708f00ba9be02289c","tid":105393,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T01:12:33.000Z","msg":"大陸有廁所架咩"},{"pid":"8e936ac3fb917cb4c82178837d1dd19f244d224d","tid":105393,"uid":20074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T01:17:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>個老母冇睇住細路<br />\n個細佬冇人教佢唔可以隨街小便<br />\n個司機埋站冇睇清楚就鏟埋去<br />\n<br />\n三樣野是但唔中一樣件事都可以避免<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n大陸人不嬲放生周街跑<br />\n大陸細佬不嬲周街小便<br />\n大陸司機不嬲周街比人上車<br />\n<br />\n三樣野其實日日係大陸發生，基本上每隔一排就有事發生，只係避免左既我地睇唔到"},{"pid":"bb2150ab49ffd8a84fd914d1aea55129c1bddb05","tid":105393,"uid":50327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T01:19:34.000Z","msg":"可能係走失咗<br />\n強國細路成日走失"},{"pid":"351d5d553d9cb4c6b2edbe2784a482ae5dacbc80","tid":105393,"uid":38744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T01:23:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>會唔會係特登教個女去馬路屙尿屈賠償<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n家屬: 應該起曬圍欄隔住條馬路同行人，防止比人行出馬路，一定係政府責任，要求賠償<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n